@startuml MyAIStorybook_SSD_Idea_Workshop
title MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Idea Workshop Scenario

actor "User" as User
participant ":System" as System

note over User, System
    Idea Workshop Scenario (Main Success)
    System is treated as BLACK BOX
end note

User -> System : startWorkshop(mode)
System --> User : workshop_started, initial_question

loop [gathering requirements]
    User -> System : provideInput(user_input)
    System --> User : acknowledgment, next_question
end

User -> System : requestStoryGeneration()
System --> User : generated_story(title, scenes[])

User -> System : endWorkshop()
System --> User : workshop_ended

note right of System
    System guides user through
    interactive story ideation
    Collects requirements internally
end note

@enduml
